SEMIFINALS

First Legs
[May 3]
Camaçari       0-2  Bahia
[May 8]
Juazeiro       1-1  Vitória

Second Legs
[May 10]
Bahia          1-3  Camaçari     [Bahia qualified due to better 1st phase]
Vitória        5-1  Juazeiro

FINALS

First Leg
[May 17]
Bahia          2-0  Vitória

Second Leg
[May 24]
Vitória        1-0  Bahia

Bahia wins the second stage.

For winning both stages, EC Bahia wins the 1998 Bahia state championship.

